results.name: Also aperiodic partitions of n into k parts
formula: Moebius transform of partition triangle A008284.
example: For n=6, 2+2+1+1 is periodic because it can be written 2*(2+1), similarly 1+1+1+1+1+1, 3+3 and 2+2+2.
xref: Row sums give A000837. Cf. A055893.
